" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mak1665702804857.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mak1665702804857.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mak1665702804857.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mak1665702804857\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Use Transactions\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether the use of transactions is enabled for the component when run in a distributed transaction processing environment. Valid values are <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> (default).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mak1665702804857__section_w47ab1b5b1_w48ab1b5_w49ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mak1665702804857__table_d560e1_d561e1_d562e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mak1665702804857__table_d560e1_d561e1_d562e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mak1665702804857__table_d560e1_d561e1_d562e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mak1665702804857__table_d560e1_d561e1_d562e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mak1665702804857__table_d560e1_d561e1_d562e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Use of transactions is disabled.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mak1665702804857__table_d560e1_d561e1_d562e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mak1665702804857__table_d560e1_d561e1_d562e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Use of transactions is enabled. To determine how transactions are applied, set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transaction Type</span>. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"swf1665702804924.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swf1665702804924.html\" title=\"Transaction mode for all operations in the component when run in a distributed transaction processing environment.\">Transaction Type</a>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mak1665702804857__section_ahn_hmf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d865502e137\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mak1665702804857__p_d6404e1_d6405e1_d6406e1\">In a distributed transaction environment, the client can\n            start a transaction, and one or more services started by the client can participate in\n            the transaction. When an operation that is located on a server is called, the server\n            switches the DBMS to this transaction, so the service works on a transaction that is\n            already started.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mak1665702804857__section_mwm_3mf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d865502e146\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"mak1665702804857__ul_sck_jmf_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mak1665702804857__li_d3116e1_d3117e1_d3118e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qnm1665702714020.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qnm1665702714020.html\" title=\"A Signature Implementation is a Development Object that defines the technology used to implement a signature, such as Uniface, COM, SOAP and so on. A Signature can have multiple implementations. Each Signature Implementation captures the technology-specific properties of the Signature, Signature Operation, and Signature Parameters.\">Signature Implementation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3636410\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3636410\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Use Transactions Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Use Transactions Determines whether the use of transactions is enabled for the component when run in a distributed transaction processing environment. Valid values are True or False (default). Value Description False Use of transactions is disabled. True Use of transactions is enabled. To determine how transactions are applied, set the Transaction Type . For more information, see Transaction Type . Description In a distributed transaction environment, the client can start a transaction, and one or more services started by the client can participate in the transaction. When an operation that is located on a server is called, the server switches the DBMS to this transaction, so the service works on a transaction that is already started. Applies To Signature Implementation Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}